{"id":305578,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/明報-廣東鶴山千人上訪暫平息2235/","date":"2013-07-26T00:02:06Z","modified":"2013-07-26T00:02:06Z","title":"明報 | 廣東鶴山千人上訪暫平息[22:35]","content":"<p><p><span>廣東江門鶴山市一村委會逾千名村民今日集體赴廣東省委上訪，在省有關方面的積極調處下，已暫時平息。</span></p>\n<div><span></p>\n<p><span>當天傍晚7時15分起，上訪村民陸續離去。</span></p>\n<p><span>新華社稱，從下午一直到傍晚，廣東省信訪及相關部門工作人員耐心聽取了村民的請願意見，承諾加大案件督辦和查處力度。村民在得到省有關部門一定的承諾後，於當天傍晚7時15分起，陸續離開上訪集結的廣東省委大院附近，大部分群眾坐由鶴山市政府組織安排的車輛回家。</span></p>\n<p><span>（新華社）</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></span></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/a/chinadigitaltimes.net/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&#038;formkey=dGlaNkplWEluYV9TWUxDQkhfaDlxQmc6MQ\" width=\"510\" height=\"334\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":1000,"categories":[18270,18269,18424],"tags":[19188,19189]}